I also have a 50 Healer that I respec into aug (44aug, 21 mend, 23 paci <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :evil --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/devil.gif ALT=":evil"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> ) and he is doing much better than my skald (he has mastery of block 3). I have no problem taking down other tanks in 1v1.<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#d1c2a2><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub36.ezboard.com/bteamskald.showUserPublicProfile?gid=svipdag@teamskald>Svipdag</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Team Skald Participant</span><br>  Posts: 10<br> <font color=#ff0000>(5/15/03 12:30:01 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=605.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Fast</span><hr size=1> @hooliganfriar<br>
