46 bsongs, 21 weap, 42 shield or 44 bsongs, 25 weap and 42 shield. Quite usefull to the team as a slam bot then. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#efe0c0><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub36.ezboard.com/bteamskald.showUserPublicProfile?gid=hooliganfriar>hooliganfriar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Team Skald Participant</span><br>  Posts: 9<br> <font color=#ff0000>(5/15/03 8:27:09 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=605.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Re:</span><hr size=1> Although the 1.5 and shield spec is my least favorite option I do see a viable  spec template for it.<br>
